For me, the @lancomeofficial Génifique serum is pure nostalgia. When I was getting together my first skincare routine ever, I remember asking my mom for help. She handed me a few travel sizes of this serum that came with her Bi-facil at the Lancôme counter. I definitely didn’t need to be using this type of serum at 15 years old, but in my thirties, it is a staple in my routine. I love the way it makes my skin look and feel, and the smell alone instantly transports me back to when I was younger. Thanks mom! Lol

In case I haven’t been clear, I am a Vitamin C fan! I used the @drunkelephant Vitamin C serum (C-Firma) many years ago and liked it, but the new formulation is so much better! By mixing the actives together, you get the most shelf stable and concentrated active ingredients. Vitamin C does not stay effective forever, so as soon as the formula is made the clock starts ticking. That means, there are serums you’re spending money on that are not at their best! The new C-Firma stops that problem! #drunk #elephant #drunkelephant #drunkelephantskincare #vitaminac #skincaretips
